Source: system-bootscreen
Section: x11
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Steph DGenius <stephanetse@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 10.5.1)
Standards-Version: 4.5.0

Package: system-bootscreen
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, plymouth, plymouth-label, plymouth-theme-spinner
Provides: plymouth-theme
Replaces: plymouth (<< 0.8.1-1~)
Description: graphical boot animation and logger
 Plymouth is an application that runs very early in the boot process
 (even before the root filesystem is mounted!) that provides a graphical
 boot animation while the boot process happens in the background.
 .
 This package contains the Kaytime splash theme for Plymouth.
